lead_paragraph: Thongchai Jaidee credited his time as a paratrooper in the Thai army for giving him the physical and mental strength to hold off Europe's finest golfers and win the French Open at the weekend.

headline.print_headline: Golfer Thongchai Says Army Training Prepared Him for French Open Win
